cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper is about reinforcement learning for robotics, which falls under the category of robotics and automation (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning models (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI) to address the challenges of RL for robotics. Additionally, the paper deals with the issue of enforcing constraints during learning, which is related to control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper uses simulation benchmarks and real-world tasks involving image processing, which are relevant to computer vision (cs.CV).
